title: VIDEO: Friday Night High School Football
text:
VIDEO: Friday Night High School Football 
By Norman Seawright III October 9, 2015 Updated Oct 9, 2015 at 10:42 PM CDT 
(NNCNOW.com) -- The final week of regular season high school football games for Minnesota—and the second to last week for Wisconsin—was highlighted by Superior's win over Eau Claire North and Cloquet's win over Duluth Marshall. 
The Spartans' third home game of the season saw them run down the Huskies 54-9, while the Lumberjacks took a 58-8 victory against the visiting Hilltoppers.
